com.att.aro.model

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.aro.model.Profile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Profile3G, ProfileLTE, ProfileWiFi

    public abstract class Profile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a device profile that is used as a model of the device when analyzing trace data.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form

      • energy

        public abstract double energy(double time1,
            double time2,
            RRCState state,
            java.util.List<PacketInfo> packets)
        A utility method for calculating RRC energy.
        Parameters:
        time1 - A beginning time value.
        time2 - An ending time value.
        state - An RRCState enumeration value that indicates the RRC energy state.
        packets - A List of packets that were passed during the specified time period. The packet information may be used in determining the amount of energy used.
        Returns:
        The energy consumed in the specified RRC state.
